Confirmed that euctl does not allow invalid JSON values:

{code:java}
[root@h-05 ~]# euctl authentication.ldap_integration_configuration='{"sync": {"enable": "false"}'
euctl: error (ModifyPropertyValueType): Failed to parse LDAP integration configuration: {"sync": {"enable": "false"} due to com.eucalyptus.auth.LicParseException: Syntax error in configuration
{code}
